_aChangeLog.text: Fixed lighting errors and light placements
fixed and cleaned up light buttons.

_aLatestUpdates._sText: This map is ready to play. I fixed most of the errors. Enjoy.

_sText:
A remake of the original crackhouse that was originally made by [GaD]Renegade a.k.a Wrenny. I added lights you can turn on and off. Added more ladders and props. I also fixed glitches. This map plays great. Have fun playing in the dark with your friends. 


A youtube video of the map.
